OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fairly
OL,6,Fcloudy evening and night with
OL,7,Foccasional mist and fog patches,
OL,8,Fperhaps the odd spot of light drizzle.
OL,9,FWinds will be light and variable.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FA mainly cloudy but dry day.
OL,12,FSome mist and fog patches are possible
OL,13,Fin the morning before conditions turn
OL,14,Fdrier and brighter from the west later
OL,15,Fon.
