OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FLargely dry and settled with light
OL,7,Fwinds. Plenty of sunshine is expected
OL,8,Fwith just a few patches of misty low
OL,9,Fcloud at times. Chance of showers by
OL,10,FFriday.
